R 3.1.1
=======

1. Install dependencies: 

 - gfortran
 - libreadline-dev
 - libcairo-dev
 - openjdk-7-jdk

2. Unpack the source, configure, and make

   tar xvzf R-3.1.1.tar.gz
   cd R-3.1.1
   ./configure --prefix=/opt/quarantine/R/3.1.1/build/ --enable-shared --with-cairo --enable-R-shlib
   make && make install
